@startuml
title Sequence Diagram - Authentication

actor User
participant "React Login Page" as Frontend
participant "Auth API Controller" as Controller
participant "Auth Service" as Service
participant "Users Repository" as Repo
participant "JWT Service" as JWT
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

User -> Frontend : Enter credentials
Frontend -> Controller : POST /auth/login
Controller -> Service : validateCredentials(dto)
Service -> Repo : findByEmail(email)
Repo -> DB : SELECT user
DB --> Repo : user
Repo --> Service : user
Service -> Service : compare password hash
Service -> JWT : create access token
Service -> JWT : create refresh token
JWT --> Service : tokens
Service --> Controller : auth response
Controller --> Frontend : tokens + user profile
Frontend --> User : Redirect to dashboard

@enduml
